name: adjnoun
description: The network of common adjective and noun adjacencies for the novel "David Copperfield" by Charles Dickens.

graph.semantic: The network of common adjective and noun adjacencies for the novel "David Copperfield" by Charles Dickens.

qares.question: which node has the highest degree in the graph?
qares.query: SELECT ?e1 WHERE { m.grap@gfb5my graph.property.contain_nodes ?e1. e1? node.property.degree ?e2} ORDER BY DESC(?e2) LIMIT 1

qares.question: what is the node with the lowest centrality in the graph?
qares.query: SELECT ?e1 WHERE { m.grap@gfb5my graph.property.contain_nodes ?e1. e1? node.property.degree_centrality ?e2} ORDER BY (?e2) LIMIT 1

qares.question: what is the node with the highest centrality that links with "room"?
qares.query: SELECT ?e1 WHERE { m.node@room node.property.connect_with ?e1. e1? node.property.degree_centrality ?e2} ORDER BY DESC(?e2) LIMIT 1

qares.question: what is the node with the lowest centrality in community 1?
qares.query: SELECT ?e1 WHERE { m.comm@ppymxf community.property.contain_nodes ?e1. e1? node.property.degree_centrality ?e2} ORDER BY (?e2) LIMIT 1
